    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在这款基于物理的建造解谜平台游戏中，你亲手放置平台，然后攀爬自己建造的结构。帮助小宝完成他从学徒到建筑大师的旅程，挑战42个精心设计的关卡，建造令人惊叹的高塔！</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>相信我，我是工程师！</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3215120/extras/5fcb143446fd5b05459b3c7c6162672d.poster.avif?t=1756887605\" width=616 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3215120/extras/5fcb143446fd5b05459b3c7c6162672d.webm?t=1756887605\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3215120/extras/5fcb143446fd5b05459b3c7c6162672d.mp4?t=1756887605\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >有没有工程学位不重要，有你在，小宝就能成功！</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>建造</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3215120/extras/0458f07ab480e59b284dc59535c2de1c.poster.avif?t=1756887605\" width=616 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3215120/extras/0458f07ab480e59b284dc59535c2de1c.webm?t=1756887605\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3215120/extras/0458f07ab480e59b284dc59535c2de1c.mp4?t=1756887605\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每个关卡都有独特挑战，你只能使用有限的物品。放置、旋转、堆叠——想办法把它们拼成一座能爬的高塔，直达顶端！</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>攀爬</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3215120/extras/70d178bc7d6b5ddfd6c3ddb3aebc620b.poster.avif?t=1756887605\" width=616 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3215120/extras/70d178bc7d6b5ddfd6c3ddb3aebc620b.webm?t=1756887605\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3215120/extras/70d178bc7d6b5ddfd6c3ddb3aebc620b.mp4?t=1756887605\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每种物品都有独特的互动方式。完成关卡后可以查看排行榜，看看自己的得分是否登顶！</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>关卡编辑器</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3215120/extras/0d67c0e4deb0627390a0e0ffae68595d.poster.avif?t=1756887605\" width=1600 height=898 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3215120/extras/0d67c0e4deb0627390a0e0ffae68595d.webm?t=1756887605\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3215120/extras/0d67c0e4deb0627390a0e0ffae68595d.mp4?t=1756887605\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >解锁关卡编辑器后，你可以自创关卡，把作品发送给朋友，或接收其他玩家的关卡，畅玩无限内容！</p>",
